A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: Great complex movie. If you are going expecting a relaunch of the old Star Wars\, check your expectations at the door. There were a couple of subplots that seemed out of place but they may play into future movies. My only complaint is i couldn’t decide when the movie was about to end. It seems to end\, then end again\, then it finally ended. It was entertaining and wrestled with the problems of both the with and Jedi.
